comments.body:
@mheon ptal

my two cents ... this notion of keeping such things in storage contradicts the idea of a container being ephemeral.  At some point, you have to capture things as an image and push to registry.  But! Volumes challenge this notion so I can certainly understand the dilemma.  My opinion is not enough to sway a good idea, so lets review it and determine the merit.  

@KayJay7 if an idea is found, are you passionate enough about the need to submit a pull request ?
